content.name: Vincent Vah Gogh
content.biography: Vincent van Gogh was a Dutch post-impressionist painter who is among the most famous and influential figures in the history of Western art.

content.name: Pablo Picasso
content.biography: Pablo Picasso was a Spanish painter, sculptor, printmaker, ceramicist, and stage designer who is widely regarded as one of the most influential artists of the 20th century.

content.name: Leonardo da Vinci
content.biography: Leonardo da Vinci was an Italian polymath of the High Renaissance who is widely considered one of the greatest painters of all time.
